reviews.review_text:
Seventh Days Between 7/41: Playin' (3:53)->Drumz (21:29)->Watchtower (5:12)->Days (10:17)->Sat Night. 

Check out the 15-minute Bird Song set one closer. Otherwise, you've got a HCS set two opener, a Playin' sandwich that culminates in The Days Between, and a LSD encore. This is a fun Vegas run, but I'm partial to the next night, 5/16.

IN THE SHADOW OF TOMORROW?? Lol.
I know 5/16 gets a lotta love, thats what even brought me to this show

But holy cow, BIRDSONG is a MUST hear version, 

Alsi, phils bass is THUNDEROUS throughout the set, dropping bombs in Birdsong jam (listen for Jerrys abrupt slamming back into the song :-)
